com.sap.conn.idoc.jco

Interface JCoIDocServerContext


  • public interface JCoIDocServerContext
    The JCoIDocServerContext provides information about a currently incoming RFC server request. This includes the current basic JCoServerContext as well as some more IDoc related context information.

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      String getFunctionName()
      Returns the called function name for processing the received IDoc package.
      String getIDocQueueName()
      Returns the inbound IDoc queue name, if available.
      char getIDocVersion()
      Returns the incoming IDoc format version.
      JCoServerContext getJCoServerContext()
      Returns the JCoServerContext object for the incoming RFC server request.
      IDocRepository getRepository()
      Returns the IDocRepository instance which was used by the JCoIDocServer for interpreting the currently received IDoc package.
